    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as your favorite pair of jeans? This beauty has been my trusty companion and is still in wonderful shape, ready to take you on your next big road trip or just handle the daily commute with ease. It's been well-loved and looked after, so you can drive away with total peace of mind. Come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019ll fall in love with how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing. This example is equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and the factory M-Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Crucially, the rear subframe mounting points have been reinforced, and the rod bearings were serviced preventatively. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis remains communicative and balanced. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited road use, the drivetrain is in excellent health, delivering linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. A driver-focused specimen for those who prioritize mechanical integrity and analog feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Reliable performance. Clean title. Maintenance up to date.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, with only minor, unavoidable stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment; the upholstery is supple, free of any tears or significant bolster wear, and all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium navigation system\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been garage-kept and serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule. Recent maintenance includes a fresh synthetic oil change, a brake fluid flush, and a comprehensive multi-point inspection confirming the suspension and drivetrain are in excellent working order. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the alloy wheels are free of curb rash. I have a complete folder of service records ready for the next owner to review. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that perfectly balances performance with everyday practicality.",
      "price": 32800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished addition to our inventory, this vehicle exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated design. Meticulously maintained and rigorously inspected, it offers a refined driving experience characterized by both performance and long-term reliability. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a high-caliber automobile that has been preserved with the utmost care. We invite serious inquiries to experience the superior standard of this well-appointed selection.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and totally ready for its next adventure with you! It drives super smoothly and has plenty of life left in it. I've taken great care of it, so you're getting a reliable car that looks and feels wonderful. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 power unit, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. The chassis remains composed with a reinforced subframe and a limited-slip variable M differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution during high-lateral-G cornering. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical integrity is robust, featuring a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a responsive suspension setup. An excellent driver\u2019s car for those valuing raw mechanical feedback and high-revving atmospheric performance.",
